      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * University of Paris</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg/330px-DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"441\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg/500px-DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg/960px-DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:DSC_6657-UniversiteMarieCurie.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Historic View of University Paris-VI <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>University of Paris</b>, <br />\nwas the university in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris\">Paris</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/France\">France</a> and one of the earliest to be established in Europe, founded in the middle of the 12th century <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Today, thirteen successor universities are split over the three academies of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%8Ele-de-France\">Île-de-France</a> region. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Organization\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Organization</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Humanities.2C_Social_Sciences.2C_Economics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Humanities, Social Sciences, Economics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Law_and_Economics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Law and Economics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Arts_.26_Humanities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Arts &amp; Humanities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Computer_Science_and_AI\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Computer Science and AI</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Organization\">Organization</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Paris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Organization\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Paris\">University of Paris</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Humanities.2C_Social_Sciences.2C_Economics\">Humanities, Social Sciences, Economics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Paris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Humanities, Social Sciences, Economics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <span id=\"1\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Paris_1_Pantheon-Sorbonne\">Paris 1 Pantheon-Sorbonne</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Law_and_Economics\">Law and Economics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Paris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Law and Economics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <span id=\"2\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Paris_II_Panth%C3%A9on-Assas\">Paris II Panthéon-Assas</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Arts_.26_Humanities\">Arts &amp; Humanities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Paris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Arts &amp; Humanities\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <span id=\"3\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Sorbonne_Nouvelle_Paris_3\">Sorbonne Nouvelle Paris 3</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"4\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris-Sorbonne_University\">Paris 4 Sorbonne University</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Computer_Science_and_AI\">Computer Science and AI</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Paris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Computer Science and AI\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <span id=